trans-unit.source: Represents a heading cell within a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en overskriften celle i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TableHeaderCell class represents a heading cell in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TableHeaderCell representerer en overskriften celle i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A> property to specify or determine the contents of the heading cell.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A>til å angi eller angi innholdet i cellen overskrift.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: This class allows you to control how the contents of the heading cell are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan du angi hvordan innholdet i overskriften celle skal vises.

trans-unit.source: The alignment of the contents in the heading cell is specified by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.HorizontalAlign%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.VerticalAlign%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Justering av innholdet i overskriften cellen angis ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.HorizontalAlign%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.VerticalAlign%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.VerticalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.HorizontalAlign%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Wrap%2A> property to specify whether the contents of the heading cell wrap in the cell.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Wrap%2A>til å angi om innholdet i den overskriften brytes i cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.Wrap%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also specify how many rows or columns in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control are occupied by an individual heading cell.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også angi hvor mange rader eller kolonner i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontrollen er opptatt med en enkelt overskrift celle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.RowSpan%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.ColumnSpan%2A> properties control how may rows and columns are used, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.RowSpan%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.ColumnSpan%2A>Egenskaper kontrollere hvor mange rader og kolonner som brukes, henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.ColumnSpan%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.RowSpan%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_abbr" name="abbr" href=""></xref> attribute of the HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_th" name="th" href=""></xref> element for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_abbr" name="abbr" href=""> </xref> attributtet HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_th" name="th" href=""> </xref> -element for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The AbbreviatedText property is rendered as the `abbr` attribute of the HTML `th` element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen AbbreviatedText gjengis som den `abbr` attributtet HTML `th` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `abbr` attribute is used by screen readers to read a shortened version of a header for each cell in the table.
trans-unit.target: Den `abbr` attributtet brukes skjermen lesere til å lese en forkortet versjon av en topptekst for hver celle i tabellen.

trans-unit.source: The AbbreviatedText property is significant for browsers that render abbreviated text in place of the content for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen AbbreviatedText er viktig for nettlesere som gjengir forkortet tekst i stedet innholdet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the abbreviated text.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer forkortet teksten.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Applies attributes to render to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Bruker attributtene for å vise til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The AddAttributesToRender method overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.AddAttributesToRender%2A> method for the base class and, in addition to calling the base method, renders the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.Scope%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.AbbreviatedText%2A> properties to the `scope` and `abbr` attribute of HTML `th` element, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Metoden AddAttributesToRender overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.AddAttributesToRender%2A>for basisklassen og i tillegg til å kalle metoden basis, gjengir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.Scope%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.AbbreviatedText%2A>egenskapene til den `scope` og `abbr` attributtet i HTML `th` elementet henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.AbbreviatedText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell.Scope%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.AddAttributesToRender%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"></xref> that receives the rendered content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter"> </xref> som mottar gjengitte innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_axis" name="axis" href=""></xref> attribute of the HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_th" name="th" href=""></xref> element for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_axis" name="axis" href=""> </xref> attributtet HTML <xref uid="langword_csharp_th" name="th" href=""> </xref> -element for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The categories can be any string values that are pertinent to the table.
trans-unit.target: Kategoriene kan være alle strengverdier som er relevante for tabellen.

trans-unit.source: The CategoryText property is rendered as the `axis` attribute of the HTML `th` element, which is used to group table cells into conceptual categories.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CategoryText gjengis som den `axis` attributtet HTML `th` element, som brukes til å gruppen celler i begrepsmodellen kategorier.

trans-unit.source: The categories are rendered in HTML as a comma-delimited list.
trans-unit.target: Kategoriene gjengis i HTML som en kommadelt liste.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: An array of string values representing the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> categories.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av streng som representerer verdier i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> kategorier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the scope of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"></xref> control when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir omfanget for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell"> </xref> kontrollerer når den gjengis.

trans-unit.source: Use the Scope property to get or set the scope of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell> control when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen området til å hente eller angi omfanget for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>kontrollerer når den gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>

trans-unit.source: The scope of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell> represents the cells that the header applies to.
trans-unit.target: Omfanget av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>representerer cellene overskriften gjelder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderCell>

trans-unit.source: For complex tables, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.AssociatedHeaderCellID%2A> property, which provides more control over the specification of the relationship of header cells to data cells.
trans-unit.target: For komplekse tabeller, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.AssociatedHeaderCellID%2A>egenskap, som gir bedre kontroll over angivelse av relasjonen celleområdet topptekst for til datacellene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell.AssociatedHeaderCellID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Scope property is used to make HTML tables more accessible by providing information about relationships between the cells and the headers.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen omfanget brukes til å gjøre HTML-tabeller mer tilgjengelig ved å angi informasjon om relasjoner mellom cellene og hodene.

trans-unit.source: For a list of the available table header scopes, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope>.
trans-unit.target: En liste over tilgjengelige tabellen hodet omfang, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope>

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope"></xref> value.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope"></xref> value.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableHeaderScope"> </xref>.
